{"tid":236832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[白色巨塔] 鄧桂思主診醫生：聯合醫院沒主動交代是重大醫療事故","createTime":"2017-05-10T04:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T17:59:57.000Z","uid":42820,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d880b93a8b009a9e18765529c93668fdf7ab11c","tid":236832,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:10:40.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】換肝病人鄧桂思的主診醫生吳國際表示，鄧桂思轉至瑪麗醫院後，他們已從醫療病歷發現聯合醫院遺漏處方預防性抗病毒藥物，他相信這是導致鄧桂思情況危殆的最主要原因，但聯合醫院並沒有主動交代，認為是重大醫療事故。<br />\n<br />\n吳國際又表示，鄧桂思情況仍然危殆，肺部被真菌感染嚴重，血液中亦種有念珠菌樣本。團隊正努力處理，但仍未能確定情況是否已受控，又表示鄧桂思使用人工肺只是權宜之計，最重要是她的肺部能自行修復。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=220602\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D220602&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=2eb96cc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D220602&h=9055ceee\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=220602</a>"},{"pid":"8273ad20335bf3b176d9289b0453bfd26fb338b5","tid":236832,"uid":78443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:22:47.000Z","msg":"真菌感染基本上都死梗咁濟"},{"pid":"dded0a3037a2ae2d35d63b7b800f8c733b3a1c13","tid":236832,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:45:52.000Z","msg":"吳醫生都唔滿意聯合醫院乜9都唔講唔交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de329343e6dab7cc1647173ca6e34d0016bea36","tid":236832,"uid":70928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T05:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a375187714b736bc4639525935fdbe9b34574dfb","tid":236832,"uid":28195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T05:18:30.000Z","msg":"盧寵茂做咩唔出句聲<br />\n<br />\n做手術之前唔係要check哂所以紀錄咩？"},{"pid":"